                TCGs, on the other hand, are designed exclusively for 2 players and have been very successful as video games. 
                Imperium is designed for 2 players and aims to simulate the TCG experience as close as possible in a deckbuilding game format. The developers believe that Imperium is the first game to accomplish this.
